metadata.footnotes: n = number of subjects; P-Y = person-years of exposure based on time to first onset. MedDRA: 27.1 Adverse events are treatment emergent AEs with an onset date on or after the first dose date of study treatment up to 30 days after the last dose date of treatment in the study.
